          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td colspan="2" class="texto2" height="219" valign="top">&nbsp;<br><p> <SPAN LANG="en-US">This translation was first published in</SPAN><SPAN LANG="en-US"><em> The Aroostook Review </em></SPAN><SPAN LANG="en-US">(Summer 2008)</SPAN>. </p>
          
            </td>
            <td rowspan="3"><img name="home_r3_c6"
 src="../../images/spacer.gif" alt="" border="0" height="368" width="16"></td>
            <td><img src="/images/spacer.gif" alt="" border="0"
